      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "A Quartet of Horns",
        "Client": "Yomogi the Chef",
        "Description": "UGH! I was gathering herbs for\r\nmy new menu out in the Sandy\r\nPlains, and guess what? Two\r\ndumb \u003CCOL RED\u003EDiablos\u003C/COL\u003E showed up to stab\r\nmy lunch dango on their\r\nhorns! Grr, I want payback on\r\nthose jerks!",
        "Target": "Hunt 2 Diablos",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Quatuor \u00E0 cornes",
        "Client": "Yomogi la chef",
        "Description": "J\u0027\u00E9tais en train de cueillir\r\ndes herbes pour ma nouvelle\r\nrecette aux Plaines de sable,\r\net deux cr\u00E9tins de \u003CCOL RED\u003EDiablos\u003C/COL\u003E\r\nm\u0027ont piqu\u00E9 mon d\u00E9jeuner !\r\nIl faut que tu me venges !",
        "Target": "Chasser deux Diablos",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Quartetto di corna",
        "Client": "Yomogi la chef",
        "Description": "ARGH! Stavo raccogliendo delle\r\nerbe alle Piane sabbiose per\r\nil mio nuovo men\u00F9 e indovina?\r\nDue stupidi \u003CCOL RED\u003EDiablos\u003C/COL\u003E hanno\r\ninfilzato i dango che avevo\r\nper pranzo con le corna! Grrr,\r\nvendicami di quegli stupidi!",
        "Target": "Caccia 2 Diablos",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "H\u00F6rner-Quartett",
        "Client": "Yomogi die K\u00F6chin",
        "Description": "PAH! Ich habe in der Sandebene\r\nKr\u00E4uter f\u00FCr neue Gerichte\r\ngesammelt, aber dann sind zwei\r\ndumme \u003CCOL RED\u003EDiablos\u003C/COL\u003E aufgetaucht und\r\nhaben meine Mittags-Dango\r\nauf ihre H\u00F6rner gespie\u00DFt! Das\r\nsollen diese R\u00FCpel b\u00FC\u00DFen!",
